tspan.tspan: Recall accuracy for query signals of varying duration (dur = 2, 4, 6, 8 seconds) and
number of bit toggles per hash frame (p = 0, 2, 4, 6, 8, 10). Bit toggles are the bit
positions to consider flipping to increase the number of candidate hashes per
frame. The table is for a threshold value, T = 0.075
